      <scopecontent id="aspace_3c19c1476bb207d08ac35cab6442bb11">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>One reel of microfilm (HM138) of scrapbooks containing miscellaneous newspaper clippings, notes and reviews of three books published by John C. Hurd: <title render="italic">
               <part>The Theory of Our National Existence</part>
            </title> (1881); <title render="italic">
               <part>The Centennial of a Revolution</part>
            </title> (1888); and <title render="italic">
               <part>The Union-State</part>
            </title> (1890).</p>  
      </scopecontent>
